"Original description:"


PREDICTOR
t               T   h         time	0	10


COMPARTMENTS
cyt             V   pl          vol.    1


STATES
RAF     C   mumol/l      conc.   cyt     1    "RAF"
pRAF    C   mumol/l      conc.   cyt     1    "pRAF"
MEK     C   mumol/l      conc.   cyt     1    "MEK"
pMEK    C   mumol/l      conc.   cyt     1    "pMEK"
ERK     C   mumol/l      conc.   cyt     1    "ERK"
